<h2>Resources</h2>

<p><strong><a href="/forums/showthread.php?t=3473738">np: RU Stage 11</a></strong> is the tier megathread for discussing the current metagame at hand.</p>
<p><strong><a href="/forums/showthread.php?t=3474174">The October Usage Stats</a></strong> list the current most used Pokemon, leads, moveset statistics, and playstyles in the tier.</p>
<p><strong><a href="/forums/showthread.php?t=3469109">The RU Senate</a></strong> thread lists the current Senate members. It also explains how to get on the rotating part of the council. If you have any questions, the Senators are the people to ask!</p>
<p><strong><a href="/forums/showthread.php?t=3471257">RU Awards and Projects</a></strong> lists awards that you can earn for posting in the RU Forum, as well as how to earn points. The thread also includes the points leaderboard for each round and the Mini-Tournament Hall of Fame.</p>
<p><strong><a href="/forums/showthread.php?t=3472279">RarelyUsed Hub</a></strong> is the thread to go to if you have any suggestions for the hub, if anything needs to be written for the hub, and to discuss news and recent updates to this site.</p>
<p><strong><a href="/forums/showthread.php?t=3455283">Ask a Simple Question Get a Simple Answer</a></strong> is the place to go if you have any questions about the tier.</p>
<p><strong><a href="/forums/forumdisplay.php?f=181">RarelyUsed Contributions and Corrections</a></strong> is the place to go for writing analyses. You may reserve an analysis in the <strong><a href="/forums/showthread.php?t=3469580">Index Thread</a></strong> or comment on analyses that are WIP.</p>

